reviewText: It did not say what language and what subtitle it was

Beatiful movie of a Saint Charbel, very few people know about this saint, his life, and the miracles. His body after death still the same, like he died yesterday. You will enjoy. The subtitles are in spanish, the movie it self is in lebanes o arabic. I don't know the lenguaje.
La vida de un santo poco conocido, sus milagros y como su cuerpo es incorruptible, como si hubiera muerto ayer. Es en árabe pero con subtítulos en español. Que lo disfruten. Santo muy milagroso de origen libanes.
